              {
                "body_blocks": [
                  {
                    "inline": [
                      {
                        "kind": "text",
                        "text": "If a is an int and less than zero, if p is not 1-dimensional, if\na is array-like with a size 0, if p is not a vector of\nprobabilities, if a and p have different lengths, or if\nreplace=False and the sample size is greater than the population\nsize."
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  }
                ],
                "data_type": "ValueError",
                "inline": [
                  {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "text": "If a is an int and less than zero, if p is not 1-dimensional, if\na is array-like with a size 0, if p is not a vector of\nprobabilities, if a and p have different lengths, or if\nreplace=False and the sample size is greater than the population\nsize."
                  }
                ],
